OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright with occasional showers
OL,6,Fduring the morning, the showers
OL,7,Fbecoming lighter and more scattered
OL,8,Fwith drier spells developing through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. The brisk west or
OL,10,Fnorthwest winds also easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry at first this
OL,13,Fevening, but thickening cloud and
OL,14,Fpatchy light rain developing.
OL,15,FOccasional mist and drizzle overnight
OL,16,Fwith winds light from the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
