OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,6,Flight rain and drizzle. Soon mainly
OL,7,Fdry and skies brightening, perhaps the
OL,8,Fodd sunny break developing. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasant in light to moderate
OL,10,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,13,Fstart on Wednesday, but rain pushing
OL,14,Fin from the northwest. Bright spells
OL,15,Fand scattered showers on Thursday,
OL,16,Fthen showers or longer outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
